snippet.title: ANACONDA – Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
I like big snakes and I cannot lie. Paul Rudd and Jack Black star in #AnacondaMovie – exclusively in theatres Christmas.

Follow Us on Social:
https://x.com/Anaconda_Movie
https://www.facebook.com/AnacondaMovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@anacondamovie
https://www.instagram.com/anacondamovie

Visit our site: https://anacondamovie.com/

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Doug (Jack Black) and Griff (Paul Rudd) have been best friends since they were kids, and have always dreamed of remaking their all-time favorite movie: the cinematic "classic" Anaconda. When a midlife crisis pushes them to finally go for it, they head deep into the Amazon to start filming. But things get real when an actual giant anaconda appears, turning their comically chaotic movie set into a deadly situation. The movie they’re dying to make? It might just get them killed

Tom Gormican​

snippet.title: SUBSCRIBER BIG WINS | EPISODE 65
snippet.description:
Welcome back to BSBZA Subscriber Big Wins Episode 65, one of the most exciting community episodes yet. This series is all about you, the viewers, and the incredible replays you send in. Episode 65 is packed with some of the best gameplay we’ve seen in a while, featuring a wide variety of titles and plenty of heart-stopping moments.

We kick things off with the candy chaos of Sugar Rush, a game that continues to dominate the big win charts thanks to its potential for retriggers and huge multiplier clusters. From there we move into Sweet Bonanza 1000, where the supercharged spins and juicy payouts take things to another level. Gates of Olympus also makes a strong showing in this episode, with Zeus delivering some incredible lightning multipliers that keep the energy high. Of course, no Subscriber Big Wins episode would be complete without Hot Hot Fruit, one of the community’s most loved games, and once again it proves why it’s a fan favourite by delivering some very memorable gameplay.

Beyond those titles, we’ve also included a mix of other fan favourites to round out the episode, making this one of the most varied and entertaining installments in the Subscriber Big Wins series. With so many different games featured, there’s something for everyone to enjoy.

Thank you again to everyone who continues to send in their replays. Your clips are the reason this series is possible, and it’s amazing to see how much variety and excitement the BSBZA community brings every week. If you’d like to feature in an upcoming episode, be sure to follow me on Instagram at bsbza_ and send your replays through via DM or the submission link in the pinned story.

This is Episode 65 of Subscriber Big Wins, and it’s filled with non-stop action from start to finish. Sit back, enjoy the ride, and let me know in the comments which game impressed you most this week.
